OL,4,CSchool funding 'becoming a catastrophe'
OL,5, The crisis of school funding in England
OL,6, is turning into a catastrophe, the
OL,7, largest teaching union has said.
OL,9,FKevin Courtney, general secretary of
OL,10,Fthe National Education Union, said
OL,11,Fschools were not absorbing budget cuts,
OL,12,Finstead many were cutting posts and
OL,13,Fincreasing class sizes.
OL,15,FHe highlighted research with his union
OL,16,Fsuggesting many schools were covering
OL,17,Fclasses with teaching assistants.
OL,19,FThe government said core school funding
